reviews.review_text: Track Corrections A quick note about the tracks on this recording… track 19 includes tuning and Cumberland Blues, all the following track titles through #25 move up one position, and track 25 becomes Hard to Handle.  BTW… it was great to hear NRPS  provide a warm-up on this recording. What fun. What memories.
